reviewText: A must see for anyone contemplating a move "back to nature" or of building their own house. The story of the author's quest to build his own dreamhouse on the river is both informative and ENTERTAINING! He covers all the pitfalls from unexpected early snow to spring blackflies. You have to admire his spirit, and the strength of his accomplishments in achieving the dream, using his ingenuity and determination. A great video for any future homeowners!
